      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pemex 亏损加剧，对新任首席执行官罗德里格斯来说是个负面信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/pemex-registers-loss-in-negative-sign-for-new-ceo-rodriguez</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于销售额下滑、汇率波动和其他因素，墨西哥石油公司的亏损在第三季度翻了一番，这对墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·辛鲍姆精心挑选的执行领导团队来说是一个负面信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/pemex-registers-loss-in-negative-sign-for-new-ceo-rodriguez</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 15:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币即将突破 3 月份创下的历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/bitcoin-btc-tops-70-000-for-first-time-since-june-as-election-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币在过去两个交易日中飙升逾 8%，使这一原始加密货币即将突破 3 月份创下的近 74,000 美元的历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/bitcoin-btc-tops-70-000-for-first-time-since-june-as-election-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 23:42:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列谈判胜过中国刺激计划 油价连续第二天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于有迹象表明以色列对黎巴嫩的攻势可能缓和，抵消了中国出台更多刺激措施的前景，油价周一延续跌势，创下两年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-29</guid>
